  "title": "PROJECT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Require experience in construction project work, preferably in plumbing and sanitary works.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Co-ordinate with Main contractor on scope of work and establishing site management policy.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Resposible to deal with relevant authorities, clients consultants, sub-contractors and suppliers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Assist in planning of work schedule, handle technical and engineering problems.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Evaluate risk assessmnet, safe work procedures and method statement to ensure that it comply with contract requirement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Check all requirement in contract document, drawings and specification to ensure that variation orders are implemented with.</p>",
